---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/accounting-aurelian/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="Aurelian Tax & Advisory | The Art of Financial Precision"
  description="Navigating complex tax landscapes with the meticulous eye of a craftsman. We transform wealth management into a strategic masterpiece."
  active="home"
  canonicalPath="/templates/accounting-aurelian"
>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative min-h-[80vh] md:min-h-[90vh] flex items-center px-au-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-au-container-max mx-auto overflow-hidden py-au-unit">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-au-gutter items-center w-full">
<div class="md:col-span-6 z-10 space-y-8">
<span class="text-au-label-md font-au-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest block reveal-on-scroll">Est. 2024</span>
<h1 class="text-au-headline-lg-mobile md:text-au-display-lg font-au-display-lg text-primary reveal-on-scroll">
                        The Art of <br/><span class="italic font-normal">Financial Precision.</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-au-body-lg font-au-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-md reveal-on-scroll">
                        Navigating complex tax landscapes with the meticulous eye of a craftsman. We transform wealth management into a strategic masterpiece.
                    </p>
<div class="flex items-center gap-6 pt-4 reveal-on-scroll">
<a href="/templates/accounting-aurelian/contact" class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-10 py-4 text-au-label-md font-au-label-md hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform flex items-center gap-2 inline-flex">
                            Book a Private Consultation
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-6 relative flex justify-end reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="w-full h-[400px] md:h-[600px] rounded-tl-[100px] rounded-br-[100px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
<img alt="Artistic representation of balance and precision with glass and stone elements" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA0F_ba0zQBBAP6HvxA3UM0qBHB2VQDO5Z5lrYt8r1LIWII0RW2np2A5Ez3R1pXB55fVzRpVmEVEtyRtx4CZc5GYMB5T1-67WETAveg9kqESY_D0CdZmLVChYzdgchEf-_XXkgq5xNhTCDpIZiGkg8G-85096Khy_JIWPcrYwAtLk-gJlYiUHC3WH_wo3QFEnYugrCqCaCzgNvh9HbsbRglM7yUgH-5uss4ahJf4WB2SRjjXYQFhd1KeRIo2k5EKi05at55xScgyBrV" />
</div>
<div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 w-48 h-48 border border-primary/10 asymmetric-border z-[-1] animate-[spin_20s_linear_infinite] hidden md:block"></div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- The Philosophy Section -->
<section class="py-au-section-gap px-au-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-au-container-max mx-auto">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-au-gutter">
<div class="md:col-start-2 md:col-span-4">
<h2 class="text-au-headline-lg font-au-headline-lg text-primary leading-tight reveal-on-scroll">
                        A Human-Centric <br/>Legacy of Craft.
                    </h2>
</div>
<div class="md:col-start-7 md:col-span-5 space-y-8">
<p class="text-au-body-lg font-au-body-lg text-on-surface reveal-on-scroll">
                        At Aurelian, we believe that wealth is not just a ledger of numbers, but a collection of life's intentions. Our approach rejects the automated, cold reality of modern accounting in favor of deep, intellectual partnership.
                    </p>
<p class="text-au-body-md font-au-body-md text-on-surface-variant reveal-on-scroll">
                        Every strategy we curate is bespoke, designed to respect both the complexity of the law and the simplicity of your lifestyle goals. We call it financial architecture — the silent support system for your grandest visions.
                    </p>
<div class="reveal-on-scroll">
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-au-label-md font-au-label-md text-primary border-b border-primary pb-1 hover:gap-5 transition-all" href="/templates/accounting-aurelian/philosophy">
                            Our Philosophy
                        </a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Services Grid -->
<section class="py-au-section-gap bg-secondary-fixed/30 relative">
<div class="px-au-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-au-container-max mx-auto">
<div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-16">
<h2 class="text-au-headline-lg font-au-headline-lg text-primary reveal-on-scroll">Disciplines of Advisory</h2>
<div class="hidden md:block w-32 h-[1px] bg-primary/20 mb-4 reveal-on-scroll"></div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
<div class="group relative p-12 bg-surface border border-outline/10 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 reveal-on-scroll">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform block">architecture</span>
<h3 class="text-au-headline-md font-au-headline-md mb-4">Strategic Tax Planning</h3>
<p class="text-au-body-md font-au-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8">Sophisticated navigation of cross-border compliance and multi-layered tax optimization strategies for the modern visionary.</p>
<div class="h-1 w-0 bg-primary group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-700"></div>
</div>
<div class="group relative p-12 bg-surface border border-outline/10 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 reveal-on-scroll">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform block">auto_awesome</span>
<h3 class="text-au-headline-md font-au-headline-md mb-4">Private Wealth Management</h3>
<p class="text-au-body-md font-au-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8">Preserving generational prosperity through holistic asset allocation, estate planning, and risk mitigation models.</p>
<div class="h-1 w-0 bg-primary group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-700"></div>
</div>
<div class="group relative p-12 bg-surface border border-outline/10 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 reveal-on-scroll">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform block">account_balance</span>
<h3 class="text-au-headline-md font-au-headline-md mb-4">Corporate Advisory</h3>
<p class="text-au-body-md font-au-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8">Agile structural guidance for boutique firms and high-growth ventures seeking sustainable, tax-efficient scaling.</p>
<div class="h-1 w-0 bg-primary group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-700"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="mt-16 text-center reveal-on-scroll">
<a href="/templates/accounting-aurelian/services" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-au-label-md font-au-label-md text-primary border-b border-primary pb-1 hover:gap-5 transition-all">
All Disciplines
</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Social Proof Section -->
<section class="py-au-section-gap px-au-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-au-container-max mx-auto overflow-hidden">
<div class="text-center mb-20 reveal-on-scroll">
<h2 class="text-au-label-md font-au-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Trusted by Visionaries</h2>
<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-16 opacity-40 grayscale contrast-125">
<span class="text-au-headline-md font-au-headline-md italic font-light tracking-tighter">LUXE.CO</span>
<span class="text-au-headline-md font-au-headline-md font-bold">MERIDIAN</span>
<span class="text-au-headline-md font-au-headline-md tracking-[0.2em] font-normal">SOMA</span>
<span class="text-au-headline-md font-au-headline-md font-serif italic">Vanguard.</span>
<span class="text-au-headline-md font-au-headline-md uppercase font-light">Elysium</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative bg-surface-container-low p-8 md:p-24 overflow-hidden reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 text-primary/5 select-none hidden md:block">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[200px]" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">format_quote</span>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl">
<p class="text-au-headline-lg font-au-headline-lg text-primary italic mb-12">
                        "Aurelian doesn't just manage my taxes; they steward my legacy. Their attention to the nuance of my creative business is unparalleled in the industry."
                    </p>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-primary"></div>
<div>
<p class="font-bold text-on-surface">Eleanor Vance</p>
<p class="text-au-caption font-au-caption text-on-surface-variant">Founder, The Obsidian Group</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Final CTA -->
<section class="px-au-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-au-container-max mx-auto mb-au-section-gap">
<div class="bg-primary-container p-8 md:p-32 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-12 group reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-xl text-center md:text-left">
<h2 class="text-au-display-md font-au-display-md text-on-primary mb-6">Begin Your Portfolio Review.</h2>
<p class="text-au-body-lg font-au-body-lg text-on-primary-container mb-10">Private consultations are conducted in complete discretion. Experience the intersection of strategy and art.</p>
<a href="/templates/accounting-aurelian/contact" class="bg-tertiary-fixed text-on-tertiary-fixed px-12 py-5 text-au-label-md font-au-label-md hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 inline-block">
                        Inquire Privately
                    </a>
</div>
<div class="hidden md:block w-96 h-96 absolute -right-20 -top-20 opacity-10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[400px] text-on-primary">grain</span>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</TemplateLayout>
